  - body: Click a nearby host to target it, then press Space to infect it.
  - body: Walkers use land, swimmers use water, and flyers can cross both while ignoring
      obstacles.
  - body: Reach the spaceship to win. Police can arrest you only while you are exposed
      in base form.
  - body: Hosts die when their timer runs out. If a swimmer dies in water, you drown
      and lose.
